{"title":"背影——给改革者","authors":["雷霆"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":11,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"背影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——给改革者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷霆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就这样你走去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前面是莺飞草长的季节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岸上的人清醒如秋虫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切充满色彩的闲言顿然泥泞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涂抹你挺动的中国红墙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长城伸展颤栗的方向久了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄河涌动澎湃的古调久了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你淌过的地方足令"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同代人竞发千帆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"某个早晨紧咬的嘴唇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽然蹦出一丝微笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如劈山之利刃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"断千年黄土幽梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"断世代民族恩怨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"断不了一条古道通向你脚跟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掏一把黄泥掉几滴泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你弓身的地方站立长久"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙骨的梦魂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铸你还会滴血的墓碑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪烁的铭文如星群"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}